{"tid":2428284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭梓健今晚訓唔訓得著？","createTime":"2021-03-01T12:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T13:45:20.000Z","uid":1707,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"33b9aa571904f1f842ce4b2f0f4e8cd19e762294","tid":2428284,"uid":1707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"#西九龍裁判法院第四庭 <br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官 #提堂<br />\n#20200525青衣 #20200724青衣<br />\n#20200804青衣<br />\n👤D1:張(16) D2:關(18) <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n🛑D3: 鄭梓健 &gt;&gt; 轉為控方證人後獲撤銷控罪 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n～此為後補資訊，非即時～<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1.刑事損壞 [D1]<br />\n於2020年5月25日，在青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學，與其他身份不詳人士無合理辯解而損毀屬於該學校之玻璃大門。 <br />\n<br />\n2.縱火罪 [D1-2]<br />\nD1-2同被控於2020年7月24日，在青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學大門外，無合法辯解而用火損壞屬於該學校大門外的花槽及牆壁。 <br />\n<br />\n4.管有攻擊性武器 [D1]<br />\nD1被控於2020年8月4日，在青衣某單位，無合法權限或合理辯解而管有攻擊性武器，即2支伸縮棍。 <br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年3月31日 09:30西九龍裁判法院第一庭再提訊，屆時將會處理轉介至區域法院的文件。 <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🟢D1、D2維持原有條件保釋<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><strong><span class=\"red\">😡D3當庭釋放，開心喇你</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n(按：對於割蓆篤灰行為表示極度遺憾）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:法座文字直播台 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt11NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=d5c6404b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"dafddfb3c041abeccfcf830ecf3349d32161f71b","tid":2428284,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858b22a2ea7d99ddce843b0ba4eb572fd5ce610e","tid":2428284,"uid":1707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787d863c685483b270d65c52a862cd23e589c50c","tid":2428284,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"篤灰"},{"pid":"47ac6611ac53f62dc6eae62b9124de470580d40e","tid":2428284,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"25仔"},{"pid":"f608761654fbde02be128516bfc30bc73d694f23","tid":2428284,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":18,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"吓 人不為己天誅地滅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十年你代佢坐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a79335992eb9192b93685f5172825214ad46745","tid":2428284,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"#6又吠"},{"pid":"f9b2fe8104c652d1e49f9d048fac5113bd53a442","tid":2428284,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"呢單係社運案件？冇跟開"},{"pid":"03cb324d74c36b3da087355fcd4ef999e044f092","tid":2428284,"uid":240031,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"原來已經有人開咗po<br />\n鄭椊健 睇你個閪樣你喺學校同將來都無運行<br />\n靠出賣戰友嘅賤畜 無人會接受你<br />\n<br />\n希望你開審做證人時誠實啲 有嗰句講嗰句<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">唔記得咗嘅就答唔記得<br />\n錯咗內容嘅亦都要出返聲<br />\n唔好主控撚鳩你話要咁講就照講</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔係教你俾假口供<br />\n只係司法公正好緊要嘛<br />\n記撚住呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"17db6309ff01adb9c6835b886291565e664742aa","tid":2428284,"uid":105891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"睇錯鄭伊麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8648033f4d38047217b0a06f24d954400c61067a","tid":2428284,"uid":126782,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"呢單都唔係社運案 啲MK仔犯法 討論來做咩"},{"pid":"e7c2aa1408bc539f67a6954b2828f843566f4114","tid":2428284,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8648033f4d38047217b0a06f24d954400c61067a","tid":2428284,"uid":126782,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"呢單都唔係社運案 啲MK仔犯法 討論來做咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"人大上年5月通過決定，授權人大常委訂立「港版國安法」，之後大家仲話公投罷工罷課，&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;5月25號第一次做嘢（破壞學校大門），之後縱火，&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;咁做想大家冇學返，點會唔係社運case？<br />\n<br />\n除非各位忘記咗叫大家公投罷工罷課呢啲事情，破壞大門同縱火，同啲人堵路目的係差唔多，想阻人返工返學，當然嗰陣已經好多連登仔笑9&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;，話6、7月都冇人冇人返學（有段時間係冇停課）<br />\n<br />\n依家幾個咁快變咗condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.我只係指出呢單係社運，我唔係話佢哋真係有做過"},{"pid":"9ba41cd4d0f972114f2483c3eaee8e14efaa8acd","tid":2428284,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7c2aa1408bc539f67a6954b2828f843566f4114","tid":2428284,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8648033f4d38047217b0a06f24d954400c61067a","tid":2428284,"uid":126782,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"呢單都唔係社運案 啲MK仔犯法 討論來做咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"人大上年5月通過決定，授權人大常委訂立「港版國安法」，之後大家仲話公投罷工罷課，&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;5月25號第一次做嘢（破壞學校大門），之後縱火，&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;咁做想大家冇學返，點會唔係社運case？<br />\n<br />\n除非各位忘記咗叫大家公投罷工罷課呢啲事情，破壞大門同縱火，同啲人堵路目的係差唔多，想阻人返工返學，當然嗰陣已經好多連登仔笑9&rdquo;佢哋&rdquo;，話6、7月都冇人冇人返學（有段時間係冇停課）<br />\n<br />\n依家幾個咁快變咗condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.我只係指出呢單係社運，我唔係話佢哋真係有做過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"哦哦...咁樣督灰都幾扑街...<br />\n<br />\nso far未聽過有人轉污點證人"},{"pid":"ded3c789f74d97d592b11607a89b1c227ff158ff",